From: Sriram Nambakam <snambakam@linux.microsoft.com>
Date: Wed, 6 May 2026 15:07:03 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 42/49] Add a Virtualization Based Security (VBS) framework. -
 Add backends for AMD SEV-SNP, Intel TDX, Arm CCA and KVM Planes. - Support
 VTL on Hyper-V in addition to Planes on KVM.

